Assuming the Information matches the Criminal Complaint in 22CF501, Defendant waives reading of Information and enters Not Guilty pleas. Court receives Not Guilty pleas in 22CF501.

State requests $10,000 cash bond- makes argument. Attorney Anderson requests signature bond or lower cash bond. Court orders $10,000 cash bond with various conditions. Time limits for preliminary hearing are waived.
